RelatedSentence: Laurel Gregory passes the time in front of the Multnomah County Recorder 's building in Portland , Or .
She is awaiting a ruling in the Marriage Equality case , so she and her partner can go into the building and get their marriage licenses .
U.S. District Judge Michael McShane in Eugene ruled the voter - approved ban unconstitutionally discriminates against same - sex couples , and he ordered the state to stop enforcing it .
